{
  "name": "TextFrame2",
  "summary": "<p>该对象包含文本框中的文本，还包含控制文本框对齐方式和位置的属性和方法。使用 <strong>TextFrame2</strong>属性可返回 <strong>TextFrame2</strong> 对象。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例在第一张工作表中添加一个矩形，向矩形中添加文本，然后设置文本框的边距。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> textFrame2 = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AddShape</span>(msoShapeRectangle, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">250</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">140</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextFrame2</span>\n    textFrame2.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextRange</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Text</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Here is some test text&quot;</span>\n    textFrame2.<span class=\"hljs-property\">MarginBottom</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>\n    textFrame2.<span class=\"hljs-property\">MarginLeft</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>\n    textFrame2.<span class=\"hljs-property\">MarginRight</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>\n    textFrame2.<span class=\"hljs-property\">MarginTop</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例判断如果活动工作表中第二个形状的文本框包含文本，则显示文本长度。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> textFrame2 = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextFrame2</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (textFrame2.<span class=\"hljs-property\">HasText</span> == msoTrue) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(textFrame2.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextRange</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Length</span>)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>代表 <strong>Shape</strong>、<strong>ShapeRange</strong> 或 <strong>ChartFormat</strong> 对象的文本框。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "Application",
      "summary": "<p>如果不与对象识别符一起使用，则该属性返回一个代表 ET 应用程序的 <strong>Application</strong>对象。如果与对象识别符一起使用，则该属性返回一个代表指定对象的创建程序的 <strong>Application</strong>对象（可将此属性与一个 OLE 自动化对象一起使用以返回该对象的应用程序）。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回 <strong>Application</strong>对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "Object",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "AutoSize",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>指定的对象的大小，可自动调整大小以适应其中包含的文字。可读/写 <strong>MsoAutoSize</strong>。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例使第一张工作表中第一个形状根据文本调整形状。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextFrame2</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AutoSize</span> = msoAutoSizeShapeToFitText\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表中第二个形状是否根据形状调整文本。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> textFrame = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextFrame2</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(textFrame.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AutoSize</span> == msoAutoSizeTextToFitShape)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "MsoAutoSize",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Creator",
      "summary": "<p>如果该对象是在 ET 中创建的，则此属性返回字符串 XCEL，它等同于十六进制的数字 5843454C。<strong>Creator</strong> 属性是为 Macintosh 上的 ET 设计的，在 Macintosh 上，每个应用程序都具有一个四字符的创建者代码。例如，ET 的创建者代码为 XCEL。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 32 位整数，该整数指示创建对象的应用程序。只读 <strong>Long</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<p>本示例显示一条有关 ET 工作簿的创建者的消息。 </p>\n<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> myObject = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (myObject.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextFrame2</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Creator</span> == <span class=\"hljs-number\">1480803660</span>) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;This is a ET object.&quot;</span>)\n    }\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;This is not a ET object.&quot;</span>)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（int4 精度）",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "HasText",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回指定文本框是否有文本。只读 <strong>MsoTriState</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例如果文本框包含文本，则设置文本框中的文本字体为“Arial”。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> textFrame2 = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextFrame2</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (textFrame2.<span class=\"hljs-property\">HasText</span>) {\n        textFrame2.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextRange</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Font</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Name</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Arial&quot;</span>\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一张工作表中第二个形状的文本框是否包含文本。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> textFrame2 = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextFrame2</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(textFrame2.<span class=\"hljs-property\">HasText</span> == msoTrue)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "MsoTriState",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "HorizontalAnchor",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置指定文本的水平定位类型。可读/写 <strong>MsoHorizontalAnchor</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将活动工作表中第一个文本框的文本设置成文本水平居中。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> textFrame2 = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextFrame2</span>\n    textFrame2.<span class=\"hljs-property\">HorizontalAnchor</span> = msoAnchorCenter\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一张工作表中第二个形状的文本框的文本水平对齐方式是否是不对齐。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> textFrame2 = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextFrame2</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(textFrame2.<span class=\"hljs-property\">HorizontalAnchor</span> == msoAnchorNone)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "MsoHorizontalAnchor",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "MarginBottom",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置从文本框底端到包含文本的形状的内接矩形底端的距离（以磅为单位）。可读/写 <strong>Single</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例在第一张工作表中添加一个矩形，向矩形中添加文本，然后设置形状文本框底部的边距为 80 磅。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> textFrame2 = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AddShape</span>(msoShapeRectangle, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">250</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">140</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextFrame2</span>\n    textFrame2.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextRange</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Text</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;这是个矩形&quot;</span>\n    textFrame2.<span class=\"hljs-property\">MarginBottom</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">80</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例在活动工作表中添加一个椭圆，向椭圆中添加文本，并显示文本框架的底部边距。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> textFrame2 = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AddShape</span>(msoShapeOval, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">200</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextFrame2</span>\n    textFrame2.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextRange</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Text</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;这是个椭圆&quot;</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(textFrame2.<span class=\"hljs-property\">MarginBottom</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（float 精度）",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "MarginLeft",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>以磅为单位返回或设置从文本框左边界到包含文本的形状中内接矩形的左边界的距离。可读/写 <strong>Single</strong>类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例在第一张工作表中添加一个矩形，向矩形中添加文本，然后设置形状文本框左边距为 50 磅。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> textFrame2 = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AddShape</span>(msoShapeRectangle, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">250</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">140</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextFrame2</span>\n    textFrame2.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextRange</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Text</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;这是个矩形&quot;</span>\n    textFrame2.<span class=\"hljs-property\">MarginLeft</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">50</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例在活动工作表中添加一个椭圆，向椭圆中添加文本，并显示文本框架的左边距。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> textFrame2 = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AddShape</span>(msoShapeOval, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">200</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextFrame2</span>\n    textFrame2.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextRange</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Text</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;这是个椭圆&quot;</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(textFrame2.<span class=\"hljs-property\">MarginLeft</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（float 精度）",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "MarginRight",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置从文本框右边缘到包含文本的形状的内接矩形右边缘的距离（以磅为单位）。可读/写 <strong>Single</strong>类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例在第一张工作表中添加一个平行四边形，向平行四边形中添加文本，然后设置形状文本框右边距为 60 磅。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> textFrame2 = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AddShape</span>(msoShapeParallelogram, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">250</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">140</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextFrame2</span>\n    textFrame2.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextRange</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Text</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;这是个平行四边形&quot;</span>\n    textFrame2.<span class=\"hljs-property\">MarginRight</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">60</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例在活动工作表中添加一个椭圆，向椭圆中添加文本，并显示文本框架的右边距。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> textFrame2 = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AddShape</span>(msoShapeOval, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">200</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextFrame2</span>\n    textFrame2.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextRange</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Text</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;这是个椭圆&quot;</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(textFrame2.<span class=\"hljs-property\">MarginRight</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（float 精度）",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "MarginTop",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置从文本框顶端到包含文本的形状的内接矩形顶端的距离（以磅为单位）。可读/写 <strong>Single</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例在第一张工作表中添加一个平行四边形，向平行四边形中添加文本，然后设置形状文本框顶部的边距为 20 磅。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> textFrame2 = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AddShape</span>(msoShapeParallelogram, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">250</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">140</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextFrame2</span>\n    textFrame2.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextRange</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Text</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;这是个平行四边形&quot;</span>\n    textFrame2.<span class=\"hljs-property\">MarginTop</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">20</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例在活动工作表中添加一个椭圆，向椭圆中添加文本，并显示文本框架的顶部边距。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> textFrame2 = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AddShape</span>(msoShapeOval, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">200</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextFrame2</span>\n    textFrame2.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextRange</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Text</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;这是个椭圆&quot;</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(textFrame2.<span class=\"hljs-property\">MarginTop</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（float 精度）",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "NoTextRotation",
